>>>
>>> So far I'm seeing this:
>>>
>>> - On 2.6.21 I mount the drive. After a while it spins down, and when I
>>> then unmount it, an error pops up in dmesg.
>>>
>>> - On 2.6.18 I can't provoke the same error. The drive doesn't appear to
